  <scopecontent id="aspace_d4111de5dcee995bd965ed55dfc0e803">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Photographs associated with the publication, 1923-1926; some were used, but most were not published. Mostly photos of Cornell University events, athletics, student activities, faculty, performances, military, rush, stunt pictures, campus views and buldings. Also contains some non-Cornell photos of actors and actresses used in the publication.</p>  </scopecontent>
